OL,3,CReview into baby's death after parents
OL,4,Caccuse health watchdog of dishonesty
OL,6,FA health watchdog has launched a
OL,7,Freview into how it handled the case of
OL,8,Fa baby girl who died after multiple
OL,9,Ffailures at a Nottingham hospital.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC) said
OL,12,Fan external investigation would take
OL,13,Fplace into its "knowledge and handling
OL,14,Fof information" relating to the death
OL,15,Fof Harriet Hawkins in 2016.
OL,17,FHarriet was stillborn in 2016 at
OL,18,FNottingham's City Hospital after a
OL,19,Ffive-day labour.
