OL,4,Caccuse health watchdog of dishonesty
OL,6,FAn independent report published 20
OL,7,Fmonths later found a catalogue of
OL,8,Ferrors contributed to her "almost
OL,9,Fcertainly preventable" death.
OL,11,FHarriet's parents, Sarah and Jack
OL,12,FHawkins, were awarded #2.8 million
OL,13,Ffollowing a settlement with Nottingham
OL,14,FUniversity Hospitals (NUH) in 2021.
OL,16,FThis came after the trust initially
OL,17,Fdenied wrongdoing, blaming Harriet's
OL,18,Fdeath on an infection.
