OL,4,Caccuse health watchdog of dishonesty
OL,6,FWhile campaigning for justice over
OL,7,Ftheir daughter's death, Sarah and Jack
OL,8,FHawkins, who used to work for NUH,
OL,9,Fsought help from the CQC, which has
OL,10,Fthe power to prosecute trusts over
OL,11,Fwrongful deaths.
OL,13,FIn an ITV documentary on the maternity
OL,14,Fscandal, "Maternity: Broken Trust",
OL,15,Fthe watchdog said it was not made
OL,16,Faware of the case for four-and-a-half
OL,17,Fyears.
