OL,4,Caccuse health watchdog of dishonesty
OL,6,FIn its right of reply statement at the
OL,7,Fend of the programme, the CQC said
OL,8,Fthis went beyond its three-year
OL,9,Fprosecution window.
OL,11,FHowever, the Hawkins called these
OL,12,F"blatant untruths" as they have
OL,13,Fevidence of emails between NUH and the
OL,14,FCQC from 2018 - within the prosecution
OL,15,Fperiod.
OL,17,FThe watchdog has now said a review
OL,18,Fwill take place which will directly
OL,19,Fwork with the family.
