OL,6,FA CQC spokesperson said: "We will be
OL,7,Fcommissioning an external review into
OL,8,Fthe CQC's knowledge and handling of
OL,9,Finformation relating to Harriet
OL,10,FHawkins' death, and our engagement
OL,11,Fwith the Hawkins family in response to
OL,12,Fconcerns about the care received at
OL,13,FNottingham City Hospital.
OL,15,F"We will be working with Jack and
OL,16,FSarah Hawkins directly to develop the
OL,17,Fterms of reference for this review and
OL,18,Fto agree next steps."
OL,20,F"We'll be watching them like a hawk"
