OL,3,CReview into baby's death after parents
OL,4,Caccuse health watchdog of dishonesty
OL,6,FJack and Sarah said a review could
OL,7,Fpotentially pave the way for a
OL,8,Fprosecution over Harriet's death, but
OL,9,Fadded they have "not got much hope".
OL,11,F"We'll be watching them like a hawk.
OL,12,FIt needs to be entirely external of
OL,13,Fthe CQC," said Jack.
OL,15,FSarah added: "It's an organisation
OL,16,Fthat's meant to protect us but we've
OL,17,Fnot got much hope."
OL,19,FJack also said he would be pursuing an
OL,20,Fapology from the CQC over their
OL,21,Fstatement in the national documentary.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
