OL,6,F"They could apologise right now for
OL,7,Ftheir right of reply. They used a
OL,8,Fnational programme to cover up," he
OL,9,Fsaid. "We will be chasing them for
OL,10,Fthat.
OL,12,F"They're (the public's) regulator, not
OL,13,Fthe hospitals' regulator, but what
OL,14,Fhave they been doing? The damage they
OL,15,Fhave caused us and so many others is
OL,16,Fhuge."
