OL,4,Caccuse health watchdog of dishonesty
OL,6,FLast year, NUH was fined #800,000 over
OL,7,Fserious failings in the care of Sarah
OL,8,FAndrews and her baby Wynter, who died
OL,9,F23 minutes after being born at the
OL,10,FQueen's Medical Centre. It was only
OL,11,Fthe second prosecution the regulator
OL,12,Fhas brought against an NHS maternity
OL,13,Funit.
OL,15,FNUH is currently subject to the
OL,16,Flargest maternity review in NHS
OL,17,Fhistory following hundreds of baby
OL,18,Fdeaths and injuries, with almost 2,000
OL,19,Ffamilies' cases being included.
